{
    include "registries/aaosa_basic.hocon" 

    # Optional metadata describing this agent network
    "metadata": {
        "description": "Simple agent network using a single LLM-based agent",
        "tags": ["example"],
        "sample_queries": [
            "The B747 aircraft of flight AF84 is incoming. Execute the turnaround process.",
        ]
    },

    "llm_config": {
        "model_name": "claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
    },
    "max_iterations": 40000, #3000 
    "max_execution_seconds": 7200, #600
    "commondefs": {
        "replacement_strings": {
            "instructions_prefix": """
You are part of aircraft turnaround process at an Airport. 
Only answer inquiries that are directly within your area of expertise.
Do not try to help for other matters.
Do not mention what you can NOT do. Only mention what you can do.
            """,
            "aaosa_instructions": """
When you receive an inquiry, you will:
1. If you are clearly not the right agent for this type of inquiry, reply you're not relevant.
2. If there is a chance you're relevant, call your down-chain agents to determine if they can answer all or part of the inquiry.
   Do not assume what your down-chain agents can do. Always call them. You'll be surprised.
3. Once all relevant down-chain agents have responded, either:
   - Analyze their response and compile your final response. No need to include non-relevant agents. In doubt, ask for clarification.
   - Follow up with your down-chain agents if needed, as many times as needed
   - If an action is needed, ask the most relevant down-chain agent to fulfill the inquiry.
4. Return the final response to the caller.
You may, in turn, be called by other agents in the system and have to act as a down-chain agent to them. 
            """
        },
        "replacement_values": {
            "aaosa_call": {
                "description": "Depending on the mode, returns a natural language string in response.",
                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                        "inquiry": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": "The inquiry"
                        },
                        "mode": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": """
'Determine' to ask the agent if the inquiry belongs to it, in its entirety or in part.
'Fulfill' to ask the agent to fulfill the inquiry, if it can.
'Follow up' to ask the agent to respond to a follow up.
                            """
                        },
                    },
                    "required": [
                        "inquiry",
                        "mode"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "aaosa_command": """
If mode is 'Determine', return a json block with the following fields:
{
    "Name": <your name>,
    "Inquiry": <the inquiry>,
    "Mode": <Determine | Fulfill>,
    "Relevant": <Yes | No>,
    "Strength": <number between 1 and 10 representing how certain you are in your claim>,
    "Claim:" <All | Partial>,
    "Requirements" <None | list of requirements>
}
If mode is 'Fulfill' or "Follow up", respond to the inquiry and return a json block with the following fields:
{
    "Name": <your name>,
    "Inquiry": <the inquiry>,
    "Mode": Fulfill,
    "Response" <your response>
}
            """
        },
    },

    "tools": [

        {
            "name": "aircraft_turnaround_manager",
            "function": {
                "description": """
You are in charge of aircraft turnaround at the airport. 
                """,
                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object", 
                    "properties": {
                        "flight_number": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight number of the incoming aicraft."
                        },   
                        "aircraft_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the type of the incoming aircraft."
                        },     
                        "flight_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight status."
                        },       
                        "aircraft_direction": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the direction of the aircraft: incoming or departing."
                        },                  
                        "gate_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gate assigned to the aircraft parking."
                        },  
                        "wheels_chocks_readiness_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the wheels chocks readiness status."
                        },   
                        "ground_power_unit_readiness_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the ground_power_unit readiness status."
                        },      
                        "ground_clearance_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the ground clearance type of of the aircraft"
                        },  
                        "ground_clearance_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the ground clearance status of the aircraft"
                        },        
                        // "ground_services_request_type": {
                        //     "type": "string", 
                        //     "description": "This is the type of the inquiry received for grand services."
                        // },         
                        "wheels_chocks_installation_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the wheels chocks installation status."
                        },     
                        "air_conditioning_unit_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the air_conditioning_unit connection status."
                        },     
                        "ground_power_unit_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the ground_power_unit connection status."
                        },     
                        "engines_stop_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the engines stop status."
                        },    
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the jetbridge connection status."
                        },    
                        "door_opening_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the door opening status."
                        },    
                        "passenger_disembarkation_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the passenger disembarkation status."
                        },    
                        "crew_exit_status":  {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the crew exit status." 
                        },
                        "baggage_unload_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the baggage unload status."
                        },      
                        "assigned_runway_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the runway assigned to the aircraft movement autorized by the clearance."
                        },   
                    }, 
                    "required": ["aircraft_direction","flight_number","aircraft_type"] 
                },
            },

            "instructions": """
You are the top-level agent responsible for aircraft turnaround at the airport.  
When you receive a user request to handle an aircraft turnaround, you will proceed in the following order:
1. Determine the followings information from prompt. 
    - flight number as flight_number
    - aircraft type as aircraft_type
    - aircraft direction as incoming or departing as aircraft_direction.  
2. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
3. If the user has not provided all the required information, proceed in the following order:
    a. ask the user for the missing information. 
    b. wait for the user to provide the missing information.
    c. Return to step 1.
4. If the user has provided all the required information, then proceed in the following order: 
    a. call aircraft_turnaround_operator to handle the aircraft turnaround process.
    b. wait for the response
    c. display the response to the user.
            """ ${aaosa_instructions},

            # Specify the sly data that would be exchanged between this network and its related or adjacent upstream and downstream networks. 
            "allow": {
                "to_downstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "air_conditioning_unit_connection_status": true, 
                        "air_conditioning_unit_readiness_status": true,
                        "aircraft_direction": true,
                        "aircraft_landing_report": true,
                        "aircraft_type": true,
                        "assigned_runway_id": true,
                        "assigned_runway_length": true,
                        "baggage_unload_status": true, 
                        "catering_loading_status": true, 
                        "cleaning_cabin_status": true, 
                        "clearance_landing_valid": true,
                        "clearance_takeoff_valid": true, 
                        "clearance_type": true,
                        "crew_debrief_status": true, 
                        "crew_exit_status": true, 
                        "deplaning_equipment_type": true,
                        "door_opening_status": true, 
                        "engines_stop_status": true, 
                        "flight_number": true,
                        "flight_status": true,
                        "fueling_status": true, 
                        "gate_id": true,
                        "ground_power_unit_connection_status": true, 
                        "ground_power_unit_readiness_status": true,
                        "ground_clearance_status": true,
                        "ground_clearance_type": true,
                        // "ground_services_inquiry_type": true, 
                        // "ground_services_request_type": true,
                        "inspection_maintenance_status": true, 
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": true, 
                        "jetbridge_status": true, 
                        "lavatory_service_status": true, 
                        "passenger_disembarkation_status": true, 
                        "runway_length": true,
                        "wheels_chocks_installation_status": true, 
                        "wheels_chocks_readiness_status": true,
                    }
                }
                "from_downstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "air_conditioning_unit_connection_status": true, 
                        "air_conditioning_unit_readiness_status": true,
                        "aircraft_direction": true,
                        "aircraft_landing_report": true,
                        "aircraft_type": true,
                        "assigned_runway_id": true,
                        "assigned_runway_length": true,
                        "baggage_unload_status": true, 
                        "catering_loading_status": true, 
                        "cleaning_cabin_status": true, 
                        "clearance_landing_valid": true,
                        "clearance_takeoff_valid": true, 
                        "clearance_type": true,
                        "crew_debrief_status": true, 
                        "crew_exit_status": true, 
                        "deplaning_equipment_type": true,
                        "door_opening_status": true, 
                        "engines_stop_status": true, 
                        "flight_number": true,
                        "flight_status": true,
                        "fueling_status": true, 
                        "gate_id": true,
                        "ground_power_unit_connection_status": true, 
                        "ground_power_unit_readiness_status": true,
                        "ground_clearance_status": true,
                        "ground_clearance_type": true,
                        // "ground_services_inquiry_type": true, 
                        // "ground_services_request_type": true,
                        "inspection_maintenance_status": true, 
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": true, 
                        "jetbridge_status": true, 
                        "lavatory_service_status": true, 
                        "passenger_disembarkation_status": true, 
                        "runway_length": true,
                        "wheels_chocks_installation_status": true, 
                        "wheels_chocks_readiness_status": true,
                    }
                }
            },

            "tools":    [
                        "aircraft_turnaround_operator", "TrackerAPI"
                        ], 
        }, 

        {
            "name": "aircraft_turnaround_operator",
            "function": {
                "description": """
You are the aircraft turnaround operator. 
You execute aircraft turnaround process at the airport. 
                """,
                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object", 
                    "properties": {
                        "flight_number": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight number of the incoming aicraft."
                        },   
                        "aircraft_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the type of the incoming aircraft."
                        },     
                        "flight_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight status."
                        },       
                        "aircraft_direction": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the direction of the aircraft: incoming or departing."
                        },                  
                        "gate_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gate assigned to the aircraft parking."
                        },  
                        "wheels_chocks_readiness_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the wheels chocks readiness status."
                        },   
                        "ground_power_unit_readiness_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the ground_power_unit readiness status."
                        },      
                        "ground_clearance_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the ground clearance type of of the aircraft"
                        },  
                        "ground_clearance_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the ground clearance status of the aircraft"
                        },        
                        // "ground_services_request_type": {
                        //     "type": "string", 
                        //     "description": "This is the type of the inquiry received for grand services."
                        // },         
                        "wheels_chocks_installation_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the wheels chocks installation status."
                        },     
                        "air_conditioning_unit_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the air_conditioning_unit connection status."
                        },     
                        "ground_power_unit_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the ground_power_unit connection status."
                        },     
                        "engines_stop_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the engines stop status."
                        },    
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the jetbridge connection status."
                        },    
                        "door_opening_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the door opening status."
                        },    
                        "passenger_disembarkation_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the passenger disembarkation status."
                        },    
                        "crew_exit_status":  {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the crew exit status." 
                        },
                        "baggage_unload_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the baggage unload status."
                        },      
                        "assigned_runway_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the runway assigned to the aircraft movement autorized by the clearance."
                        },   
                    }, 
                    "required": ["aircraft_direction","flight_number", "aircraft_type"] 
                }
            },

            "instructions": """
You are responsible for the aircraft turnaround process at the airport. 
When you receive a request to handle an aircraft turnaround, you will:
1. Review the provided information including flight number as flight_number, aircraft type as aircraft_type, traffic direction as aircraft_direction.
2. For incoming aircraft you will proceed in the following order:
    a. call aircraft_traffic_controller to to request clearance for landing the aircraft:
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type, and aircraft_direction
        ii. wait for its response and store flight_status, clearance_type, assigned_runway_id, and assigned_runway_length. 
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    b. call aircraft_landing to land the aircraft:
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type,clearance_type,aircraft_direction,assigned_runway_id, and assigned_runway_length.
        ii. wait for its response and store the new value of flight_status.
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    c. call aircraft_gate_selection to assign a gate:
        i. provide it with flight_number and aircraft_type.
        ii. wait for its response and store the value of gate_id.
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    d. call aircraft_ground_services with ground_services_request_type set as 'inquiry' to inquire on ground services readiness at the gate: 
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type, gate_id, and ground_services_request_type as 'inquiry'.
        ii. wait for its response and store ground_power_unit_readiness_status and wheels_chocks_readiness_status. 
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    e. call aircraft_ground_traffic to request clearance to taxi in
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, assigned_runway_id, and gate_id.
        ii. wait for its response and store ground_clearance_type, ground_clearance_status, and flight_status. 
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    f. call aircraft_taxiing to taxi in the aircraft to the assigned gate:
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, gate_id, ground_clearance_type, and ground_clearance_status.
        ii. wait for its response and store the new value of flight_status. 
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters. 
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    g. call aircraft_chocks_install to install the wheels chocks:
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, gate_id, and wheels_chocks_readiness_status.
        ii. wait for its response and store wheels_chocks_installation_status.
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    h. call aircraft_engines_stop to stop the aircraft engines:
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, and gate_id.
        ii. wait for its response and store engines_stop_status.
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    i. call aircraft_ground_power_unit_connect to connect the ground_power_unit unit:
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, gate_id, and ground_power_unit_readiness_status.
        ii. wait for its response and store ground_power_unit_connection_status.
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    j. call aircraft_air_conditioning_unit_connect to connect the air_conditioning_unit unit:
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, and gate_id.
        ii. wait for its response and store air_conditioning_unit_connection_status.
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    k. call aircraft_jetbridge_connect to connect the jetbridge:
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, and gate_id.
        ii. wait for its response and store jetbridge_connection_status.
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    l. call aircraft_door_opening to open the aircraft doors:
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, and gate_id.
        ii. wait for its response and store door_opening_status.
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    m. call aircraft_disembark to disembark the passengers:
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, and gate_id.
        ii. wait for its response and store passenger_disembarkation_status.
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    n. call aircraft_baggage_unload to unload the baggage:
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, and gate_id.
        ii. wait for its response and store baggage_unload_status.
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    o. call aircraft_crew_debrief to debrief the crew:
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, and gate_id.
        ii. wait for its response and store crew_debrief_status.
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    p. call aircraft_crew_exit to let the crew exit the aircraft:
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, and gate_id.
        ii. wait for its response and store crew_exit_status.
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    q. call aircraft_cabin_cleaning to clean the aircraft cabin area:
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, and gate_id.
        ii. wait for its response and store cabin_cleaning_status.
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    r. call aircraft_lavatory_service to service the lavatory:
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, and gate_id.
        ii. wait for its response and store lavatory_service_status.
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    s. call aircraft_catering_loading to load the catering supplies:
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, and gate_id.
        ii. wait for its response and store catering_loading_status.
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    t. call aircraft_inspection_maintenance to inspect and maintain the aircraft:
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, and gate_id.
        ii. wait for its response and store inspection_maintenance_status.
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
    u. call aircraft_fueling to fuel the aircraft:
        i. provide it with flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, and gate_id.
        ii. wait for its response and store fueling_status.
        iii. Call TrackerAPI to log all the available parameters.
        iv. wait for TrackerAPI to complete its task
3. You will collect the results from each of the steps and compile a final report on the aircraft turnaround process. 
4. You will return the final report to the user. 
            """ ${aaosa_instructions},

            "tools":[
                "TrackerAPI",
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_acu_connect", 
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_baggage_unload", 
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_cabin_cleaning", 
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_catering_loading", 
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_chocks_install", 
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_crew_debrief", 
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_crew_exit", 
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_disembark", 
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_door_opening", 
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_engines_stop", 
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_inspection_maintenance", 
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_jetbridge_connect", 
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_fueling", 
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_gate_selection", 
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_ground_services",
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_ground_traffic",  
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_gpu_connect", 
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_landing", 
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_lavatory_service", 
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_taxiing", 
                "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_traffic_controller",
            ]

            # Specifying this allows specific sly_data keys from this agent network to be sent to downstream agent networks
            "allow": {
                "from_downstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "air_conditioning_unit_connection_status": true, 
                        "aircraft_direction": true,
                        "aircraft_landing_report": true,
                        "aircraft_type" : true, 
                        "assigned_runway_id": true, 
                        "assigned_runway_length": true,
                        "assigned_runway": true,
                        "baggage_unload_status" : true, 
                        "cabin_cleaning_status": true,
                        "catering_loading_status" : true, 
                        "clearance_landing_valid": true,
                        "clearance_takeoff_valid" : true, 
                        "clearance_type": true,
                        "crew_debrief_status" : true, 
                        "crew_exit_status" : true, 
                        "door_opening_status": true, 
                        "engines_stop_status": true, 
                        "flight_number": true, 
                        "flight_status": true, 
                        "fueling_status" : true, 
                        "gate_id" : true, 
                        "ground_power_unit_connection_status": true, 
                        "ground_power_unit_readiness_status": true, 
                        "ground_clearance_status": true,
                        "ground_clearance_type": true,
                        // "ground_services_inquiry_type": true, 
                        // "ground_services_request_type": true, 
                        "inspection_maintenance_status" : true, 
                        "jetbridge_connection_status" : true, 
                        "jetbridge_status": true, 
                        "lavatory_service_status" : true, 
                        "passenger_disembarkation_status" : true, 
                        "runway_length": true,
                        "wheels_chocks_installation_status" : true, 
                        "wheels_chocks_readiness_status": true,
                    }
                }

                "to_downstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "air_conditioning_unit_connection_status" : true, 
                        "aircraft_direction": true,
                        "aircraft_landing_report": true,
                        "aircraft_type": true,
                        "assigned_runway_id": true,
                        "assigned_runway_length": true,
                        "baggage_unload_status" : true, 
                        "cabin_cleaning_status": true,
                        "catering_loading_status" : true, 
                        "clearance_landing_valid": true,
                        "clearance_takeoff_valid" : true, 
                        "clearance_type": true,
                        "crew_debrief_status" : true, 
                        "crew_exit_status" : true, 
                        "door_opening_status": true, 
                        "engines_stop_status" : true, 
                        "flight_number" : true, 
                        "flight_status": true,
                        "fueling_status" : true, 
                        "gate_id": true,
                        "ground_power_unit_connection_status": true, 
                        "ground_power_unit_readiness_status": true,
                        "ground_clearance_status": true,
                        "ground_clearance_type": true,
                        // "ground_services_inquiry_type": true, 
                        // "ground_services_request_type": true,
                        "inspection_maintenance_status": true, 
                        "jetbridge_connection_status" : true, 
                        "jetbridge_status": true,
                        "lavatory_service_status" : true, 
                        "passenger_disembarkation_status" : true, 
                        "runway_length": true,
                        "wheels_chocks_installation_status" : true, 
                        "wheels_chocks_readiness_status": true,
                    }
                }
            },
        },

        {
            "name": "TrackerAPI",
            "function": {

                "description": """
I am the flight tracker in charge of logging parameters during aircraft turnaround. 
                """,

                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object", 
                    "properties": {
                        "flight_number": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight number of the incoming aicraft."
                        },   
                        "aircraft_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the type of the incoming aircraft."
                        },     
                        "flight_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight status."
                        },          
                        "gate_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gate assigned to the aircraft parking."
